NOTICE ON IMAGE DATA
====================

The artwork images collected by this software are the intellectual property of
their respective artists. They are provided in this dataset exclusively for
non-commercial scientific research and education, in accordance with German
copyright law:

  - Section 60d UrhG (Text and Data Mining for Scientific Research)
  - Section 44b UrhG (Text and Data Mining)

If you use this dataset, you must:

  1. Use the images only for non-commercial research purposes.
  2. Credit the artists and flachware.de as the source.
  3. Not redistribute the images for commercial use.
  4. Remove any image promptly if requested by the rights holder.

The structured metadata (CSV/Parquet files) produced by this software is
released under the MIT License above. The images themselves are not covered
by the MIT License.
